    "description": "FIPS Approved algorithms (relies on loaded applications): AES (Cert. #1412); RSA (Cert. #688); SHS (Cert. #1282) LaserCard LCCIDProtect is a cryptographic module based on the Athena OS755 Java Card smart card operating system with 72Kbyte of EEPROM. LCCIDProtect is compliant with the latest Java Card 2.2.2 and GlobalPlatform 2.1.1 specifications. LCCIDProtect exposes PKI and biometric APIs and is designed for high performance government and enterprise smart card applications.",
